 æ%  Dytran is an explicit finite element analysis (FEA) solution for         æ%
 æ%  analyzing complex nonlinear behavior involving permanent deformation     æ%
 æ%  of structures. Dytran enables you to study the structural integrity of   æ%
 æ%  designs to ensure that final products stand a better chance of meeting   æ%
 æ%  customer safety, reliability, and regulatory requirements.               æ%
 æ%                                                                           æ%
 æ%  With increased demand for safety and reliability of products,            æ%
 æ%  companies see a need for additional testing. However, destructive        æ%
 æ%  testing of physical prototypes is expensive and time consuming. While    æ%
 æ%  simulation can provide a solution, it is also important to use the       æ%
 æ%  right solution that is robust and accurate.                              æ%
 æ%                                                                           æ%
 æ%  Dytran delivers a structural, material flow and coupled FSI              æ%
 æ%  capabilities in a single package. Dytran↓ s explicit nonlinear solver     æ%
 æ%  technology is ideal for extreme, short-duration events and allows you    æ%
 æ%  simulate models that involve high degree of nonlinearities ‼  material,   æ%
 æ%  geometric and boundary condition nonlinearities. Dytran uses a unique    æ%
 æ%  coupling feature that enables integrated analysis of structural          æ%
 æ%  components with fluids and highly deformed materials in one continuous   æ%
 æ%  simulation.                                                              æ%
 æ%                                                                           æ%
